{"tid":1259043,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"搶客！恒生銀行取消戶口最低結餘服務月費","createTime":"2019-06-26T11:58:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T16:45:40.000Z","uid":99885,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"43de2d49830ebf740aa1e9cfaef78492c77b8620","tid":1259043,"uid":99885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T11:58:15.000Z","msg":"恒生銀行(00011)公布，將由2019年8月1日起，取消優進理財、綜合戶口，以及個人港元儲蓄戶口的最低結餘服務月費。 <br />\n<br />\n同時，該行對於ATM存摺或結單儲蓄戶口，取消現時每項20元的轉帳及現金提款櫃位服務費，而且現時每位客戶每月透過分行櫃位辦理多於50宗交易，所收取的每宗30元港元戶口交易費將會取消。 <br />\n<br />\n恒生執行董事兼零售銀行及財富管理業務主管關穎嫺表示，該行大部分個人銀行客戶，將可受惠於有關收費的取消。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190626/mobile/bkn-20190626190543952-0626_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190626%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190626190543952-0626_00842_001.html&d=DodTvzQjJx20NomtZcTkrhAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=10bf1098\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190626/mobile/bkn-20190626190543952-0626_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"6555a7e93a406b3dc4e5470d51bf9d81b5be8d98","tid":1259043,"uid":34515,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T11:59:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">［置頂］今晚八點 中環愛丁堡廣場見！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1258685\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1258685</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span>"},{"pid":"7a2843f81713dd47ace634d9d6e48779fb172e44","tid":1259043,"uid":32577,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T12:00:44.000Z","msg":"用緊恆生達啲轉去獅子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1622cf6b86d7bdb9040e6fa9ec10e3fb87f11ff","tid":1259043,"uid":103759,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T12:03:44.000Z","msg":"匯豐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"h